GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_CaseStudies> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_CaseStudies> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#CaseStudies> ;
    narr:childCount "20"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "d1b09a828565de86" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers aswritten's real-world engagements, and the dominant axis is the contrast between a converted enterprise pilot and a stalled solo prospect. [the enterprise customer's bulk-mail build](narr:CaseStudy_EnterpriseCustomerBulkMail) is the deepest case: 60 markdown docs ingested AI-to-AI, cross-platform MCP validation, and [convergence on ARB-to-memory within nine days](narr:Narrative_EnterpriseCustomerWeekOneConvergence). It [became the first paying team customer on 2026-03-26](narr:Narrative_FirstPayingTeamCustomer), with [QA onboarding named the killer demo](narr:SolutionArchetype_QAOnboarding) and the customer's chief architect's [\"clone me\" delegation pain](narr:Obs_CustomerArchitectCloneMeQuote) firing the buy trigger. Against this, [an early prospect](narr:Actor_EarlyProspect_MVPRef) — the Knowledge Packager archetype and [planned first pilot](narr:Narrative_EarlyProspectFirstPilot) — [stalled in March: neither solo-pain nor delegation trigger firing](narr:Obs_EarlyProspectMar22Text). [Scarlet reads the enterprise customer and an engineering manager at the customer as the same structural pattern](narr:Obs_CustomerArchitectEnterpriseCustomerFitsPattern). Adjacent cases span [Elephant Collective's SMS-driven events](narr:Observation_ElephantCollective), [a founder beta user's beta + VC intro](narr:Outcome_BetaCommitment), and usage-archetype observations.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Actor_EarlyProspect_MVPRef> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#CaseStudy_EnterpriseCustomerBulkMail> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DeliveryGate> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_EnterpriseCustomerWeekOneConvergence> ;
